  <brief_title>Tranexamic Acid on Blood Loss and Transfusion in Cardiac Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter Clinical Trial of Tranexamic Acid on Blood Loss and Allogeneic Transfusions in Cardiopulmonary Bypass Cardiac Surgery</official_title>
