  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Rheumatic or recessive valvular disease patients requiring valvular replacement
             surgery with cardiopulmonary bypass

          -  Coronary artery disease patients requiring coronary artery bypass surgery with
             cardiopulmonary bypass

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Non-primary cardiac surgery

          -  Definite liver and renal dysfunction

          -  Disorder in coagulation function

          -  Drugs or interventions influencing inflammatory status such as ulinastatin

          -  Allergy

          -  Pregnancy and lactation

          -  Disabled in spirit or law

          -  Fatal conditions such as tumour
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
